            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Death and the curse were in our cup,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Christ, ’twas full for Thee!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But Thou hast drained the last dark drop—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis empty now for me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That bitter cup—love drank it up;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now blessings’ draught for me."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jehovah lifted up His rod,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Christ, it fell on Thee!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thou wast sore stricken of Thy God;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There’s not one stroke for me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy tears, Thy blood, beneath it flowed;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy bruising healeth me."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The tempest’s awful voice was heard,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Christ, it broke on Thee!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy open bosom was my ward,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It braved the storm for me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy form was scarred, Thy visage marred;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now cloudless peace for me."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jehovah bade His sword awake,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Christ, it woke ’gainst Thee!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy blood the flaming blade must slake;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy heart its sheath must be—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All for my sake, my peace to make;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now sleeps that sword for me."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For me, Lord Jesus, Thou hast died,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And I have died in Thee;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thou’rt ris’n: my bands are all untied,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And now Thou liv’st in me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When purified, made white, and tried,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy glory then for me!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
